## 3. Component Catalog

### Cards

**`.card`** -- primary content container:

```
@apply rounded-2xl border border-border bg-elevated shadow-card;
```

**`.card-hover`** -- extends `.card` with lift on hover:

```
@apply card transition-all duration-200;
/* hover: shadow-card-hover + translateY(-1px) */
```

**`.modal`** -- overlay panel:

```
@apply rounded-2xl border border-border bg-elevated shadow-modal backdrop-blur-xl;
```

### Buttons

All buttons are **pill-shaped** (`rounded-full`).

**`.btn`** -- default:

```
@apply inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-border
       bg-elevated px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-text transition-all duration-150
       hover:bg-hover hover:border-border-hover
       disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed;
```

**`.btn-primary`** -- solid violet:

```
@apply border-accent bg-accent text-white
       hover:bg-accent-hover hover:border-accent-hover;
```

**`.btn-ghost`** -- transparent:

```
@apply border-transparent bg-transparent text-secondary
       hover:bg-hover hover:text-text;
```

**`.btn-danger`** -- soft red:

```
@apply border-transparent bg-danger-soft text-danger;
```

**Icon button** (inline pattern):

```
class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full
       text-secondary hover:text-text hover:bg-hover transition-colors"
```

### Form inputs

**`.form-input`**:

```
@apply w-full rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface px-4 py-2.5 text-text
       placeholder:text-tertiary
       focus:border-accent focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent/30;
```

### Tags

Use `<TagPill>` component for all tag rendering. Auto-assigns color from hash.

- Default: `rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium` with colored bg/text
- Removable: adds X button via `onRemove` prop

### Tables

Wrap in `.card overflow-hidden`. Rows representing navigable entities use `.row-link` for full-row clickability:

```html
<div class="card overflow-hidden">
  <table class="w-full text-left">
    <thead>
      <tr class="border-b border-border">
        <th class="px-6 py-3.5 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-tertiary">...</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody class="divide-y divide-border">
      <tr class="row-link" onClick={() => navigate(url)} role="link" tabIndex={0}>
        <td class="px-6 py-4">...</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
```

### Skeleton Loading

Use components from `src/components/ui/Skeleton.tsx`:

- `<SkeletonLine>` -- configurable width/height shimmer bar
- `<SkeletonCard>` -- card-shaped placeholder
- `<SkeletonTable>` -- header + N rows of shimmer
- `<SkeletonGrid>` -- grid of SkeletonCards

### View Switcher

Use `<ViewSwitcher>` from `src/components/ui/ViewSwitcher.tsx`:

- Three modes: `grid`, `list`, `table`
- Active button gets `bg-accent-soft text-accent`
- Persist user preference in localStorage

### Sketch Card

Use `<SketchCard>` from `src/components/ui/SketchCard.tsx`:

- Rich card with waveform preview, title, BPM/key, tags
- Hover: scale + shadow lift + reveal play/action overlay

### Drop zones

```
border-2 border-dashed border-border bg-surface rounded-2xl
hover:border-accent/50 hover:bg-accent/[0.075]
```

Active (drag-over): `border-accent bg-accent-soft`

> Note: `accent-soft` is a pre-baked rgba color and cannot use `/opacity`. Use `bg-accent/[0.075]` to get a half-intensity version.

### Modals

Overlay backdrop: `fixed inset-0 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-sm z-[100]`

Panel: `.modal` class. Max widths: `max-w-[400px]` for settings, `max-w-[480px]` for upload.

### Dropdowns / popovers

```
class="absolute top-full left-0 mt-1 py-1 rounded-xl
       bg-elevated border border-border shadow-modal z-10 min-w-[140px]"
```

Items: `px-3 py-2 text-sm text-text hover:bg-hover rounded-lg`.

