## 4. Layout Rules

### Navigation

**Collapsible sidebar** (`src/components/ui/Sidebar.tsx`):

- **Expanded (240px)**: Brand "artjr" + Upload button + nav links (icon + label) + collections list + Lock/Collapse at bottom
- **Collapsed (60px)**: Brand "a" + icon-only nav + compact collection icons
- Persist state in `localStorage('sidebar-collapsed')`
- Active nav item: `bg-hover text-text` with accent icon
- Fixed position, full height, `border-r border-border bg-surface`

### Page wrapper

Main content area in AppLayout:

```
class="p-8 lg:p-12 max-w-6xl w-full mx-auto"
```

Margin-left transitions with sidebar: `ml-[240px]` or `ml-[60px]`.

### Page transitions

`<PageTransition>` wraps `<Outlet />` using framer-motion:

- Slide-in: `x: 12 -> 0`, `opacity: 0 -> 1`
- Duration: 200ms, ease-out

### Top progress bar

`<TopProgressBar>` shows 2px violet bar on route changes.

### Section spacing

- Between major sections: `space-y-12`
- Default sections: `space-y-6`
- Inside forms/modals: `space-y-4` to `space-y-5`

### Card inner padding

- Content blocks: `p-6` or `p-8`
- Table rows: `px-6 py-3.5` (header) or `px-6 py-4` (body)
- Grid cards: `p-5` or `p-6`
- Modal panels: `px-5 pb-5`

### Grids

Responsive grid:

```
class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5"
```

### Max widths

| Context | Max width |
|---------|-----------|
| Page content | `max-w-6xl` (1152px) |
| Settings modal | `max-w-[400px]` |
| Upload modal | `max-w-[480px]` |
| Gate form | `max-w-sm` (384px) |

